  <!-- scenario description

    This uses the SimpleSimulation project, which creates a single player.

    To recreate:

    - Calibrate offset, mouse to upper left corner of a window, press F3
    - Operate DUECA/DUSIME state machine to advance
    - Click once to the right, once to the left, in stick window
      - Take a snapshot
    - Operate to off and exit
  -->
